1
00:00:57,159 --> 00:00:58,840
This bandit just won't mend his ways

2
00:00:59,359 --> 00:01:00,799
And now he tries to desert

3
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:03,640
Tell me, doesn't he deserve to die?

4
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,439
He deserves it! He deserves it!

5
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,000
Alright then

6
00:01:07,599 --> 00:01:08,599
Carry the body

7
00:01:08,959 --> 00:01:09,799
Back to the military camp

8
00:01:22,439 --> 00:01:22,920
Master

9
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:23,439
Auntie Xiaoling

10
00:01:23,599 --> 00:01:24,200
I'm heading off too

11
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:26,760
It's fine

12
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:27,680
I'm leaving now

13
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,319
Company Commander Shui

14
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:47,480
Wait for me

15
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:49,439
You two go on ahead

16
00:01:52,959 --> 00:01:54,359
Not bad, brother

17
00:01:54,359 --> 00:01:55,000
You're a real pal

18
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:58,120
You can help out the woman I like,

19
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,840
but I can't help out yours?

20
00:02:00,359 --> 00:02:01,120
You mean Xiaolian?

21
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:02,519
She's my sister

22
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,200
Not your real sister, though

23
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:06,959
Your sweetheart, more like

24
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:07,840
No way, no way

25
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:09,639
We know each other too well

26
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:10,879
When I was little, I was afraid of the dark

27
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:12,479
She used to go to the bathroom with me

28
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:14,080
So what?

29
00:02:16,719 --> 00:02:17,680
You're just afraid she'll

30
00:02:18,039 --> 00:02:19,280
think yours is too small

31
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,159
You're the small one!

32
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,960
What the hell do I keep you around for?

33
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:27,039
It's been days now

34
00:02:27,879 --> 00:02:29,120
A tiny little Yin-Yang Crossing

35
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,120
A speck of a town

36
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,879
A whole brigade of soldiers

37
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,319
And you can't find two people?

38
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,680
I feed you all

39
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,560
to work,

40
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,719
not to just stuff your faces.

41
00:02:38,199 --> 00:02:39,400
A bunch of good-for-nothings

42
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:40,840
Brigade Commander

43
00:02:41,199 --> 00:02:42,800
As they say, man proposes,

44
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,280
God disposes

45
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,439
What do you mean?

46
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:48,000
Spit it out clearly

47
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:49,759
Your failure to catch them

48
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:51,520
is because your fortune isn't boosted yet

49
00:02:51,759 --> 00:02:53,400
Once your fortune comes, it'll all work out

50
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:56,919
Then hurry up and boost my fortune!

51
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,759
I've scouted a grave site for Young Master

52
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,639
and found an auspicious location

53
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:04,479
If we bury Young Master and Young Mistress

54
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,840
together here, it will boost your fortune

55
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,560
Then bury them quickly

56
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,479
What are you waiting for?

57
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:11,840
Wait

58
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,800
You just said

59
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:15,439
Young Mistress

60
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:20,479
Qiuying's birth chart matches Young Master

61
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,520
But she's still

62
00:03:25,599 --> 00:03:26,960
You mean

63
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:28,840
A ghost marriage

64
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,159
Good

65
00:03:35,759 --> 00:03:36,759
All of you, get the hell out!

66
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:38,319
Yes, sir

67
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,840
Let's go

68
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,639
Why'd you stop me back there?

69
00:03:47,919 --> 00:03:48,800
If I hadn't stopped you

70
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,199
you'd be in a ghost marriage with Qiuying

71
00:03:50,199 --> 00:03:51,039
That'd be perfect

72
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,520
If we can't be together in life,

73
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,000
let us be together in death

74
00:04:00,879 --> 00:04:01,719
What are you doing?

75
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:03,400
You two playing Butterfly Lovers now?

76
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,719
Gonna turn into butterflies?

77
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:12,960
Dongsheng

78
00:04:15,479 --> 00:04:16,480
I'm begging you

79
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:18,600
Think of something

80
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,360
Help me save Qiuying

81
00:04:21,199 --> 00:04:21,879
Brother

82
00:04:22,759 --> 00:04:23,879
There's really nothing I can do.

83
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,240
But

84
00:04:28,199 --> 00:04:29,360
I can call in my expert

85
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:34,839
Who?

86
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:35,759
Master

87
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,560
You're taking advantage of me again

88
00:04:42,279 --> 00:04:43,000
Thank you

89
00:04:58,879 --> 00:04:59,720
Qiuying

90
00:05:01,199 --> 00:05:01,920
Qiuying

91
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,319
Qiuying

92
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,360
Qiuying

93
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,319
Don't go.

94
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:14,040
I'll protect you.

95
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:17,439
O world, what is love?

96
00:05:18,399 --> 00:05:20,160
It's enough to make me sick.

97
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:24,079
Do you really have to play along like that?

98
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:25,199
Who's behind this?

99
00:05:25,759 --> 00:05:27,800
Who came up with such a wicked idea?

100
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:29,319
It's a Daoist Priestess

101
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,360
Brigade Commander calls her Immortal Master

102
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,199
When's it happening?

103
00:05:35,319 --> 00:05:36,160
Tomorrow night, the Hour of the Rat

104
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,240
That soon?

105
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:40,319
Brigade Commander rushes to use his son's

106
00:05:40,319 --> 00:05:41,480
grave site to boost his career fortune.

107
00:05:42,319 --> 00:05:44,959
Ancestral tombs usually boost descendants,

108
00:05:45,199 --> 00:05:47,680
but a son boosting his father is a first.

109
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:49,800
Master

110
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:52,120
You absolutely have to help with this.

111
00:05:53,079 --> 00:05:54,959
Shuisheng once saved Xiaolian's life.

112
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,720
You saw it with your own eyes.

113
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,279
I know.

114
00:05:59,160 --> 00:05:59,680
Look,

115
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:02,240
have Shuisheng come by tomorrow at noon.

116
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,839
I need to tell him something in person.

117
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,600
There's no time, Master.

118
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,160
Quit rushing me.

119
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,759
Whatever it is, tell me.

120
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:11,240
I'll pass it along.

121
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:13,800
I mean, I need time to prepare too.

122
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,079
Hold on,

123
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,240
what do you mean by "oh"?

124
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,199
Nothing, really.

125
00:06:22,519 --> 00:06:24,360
It's just a filler word.

126
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,920
You're not gonna "oh" all night, are you?

127
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:39,120
Well, I could, Master.

128
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,800
So now you're not in a hurry?

129
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:54,000
I...

130
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,279
Where's my flask?

131
00:07:02,519 --> 00:07:03,399
Master

132
00:07:03,639 --> 00:07:04,639
What took you so long?

133
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:05,920
Shuisheng's been worried sick.

134
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,120
Kid, kid.

135
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:08,480
No, no, no.

136
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,279
I'm begging you on my knees.

137
00:07:09,279 --> 00:07:09,680
What are you...

138
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:10,639
What's going on?

139
00:07:10,639 --> 00:07:11,519
Please, save Qiuying.

140
00:07:12,399 --> 00:07:12,680
Yes.

141
00:07:12,959 --> 00:07:13,680
Get up, get up.

142
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,079
I know you're anxious.

143
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:16,800
But

144
00:07:17,079 --> 00:07:18,680
I was out handling some business.

145
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,800
There's no hurdle we can't get over.

146
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:20,920
Dropping to your knees like that

147
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:21,800
nearly gave me a heart attack.

148
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,000
Shuisheng

149
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,839
I want to ask you something.

150
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:34,639
Would you live in hiding for that girl?

151
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,040
I'm an orphan.

152
00:07:37,399 --> 00:07:38,439
I've had no ties since I was a child.

153
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:39,439
I'm willing.

154
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,079
Good

155
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:41,879
And what about the girl?

156
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:42,879
Qiu...

157
00:07:42,879 --> 00:07:43,360
Qiuying?

158
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,519
Qiuying...

159
00:07:44,639 --> 00:07:45,839
She already resents her parents.

160
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,639
They tried to elope just days ago.

161
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,759
She's a loyal and devoted person.

162
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:52,759
Shuisheng

163
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:55,519
You're asking me, Lao Jiugui, for this favor,

164
00:07:56,279 --> 00:07:57,199
and of course I'll help.

165
00:07:58,439 --> 00:08:00,279
But I can only do my best.

166
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,759
This ghost marriage...

167
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:03,199
still has to go ahead.

168
00:08:04,279 --> 00:08:05,279
Master, what are you...

169
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,240
Come here, come here.

170
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:21,720
Shuisheng

171
00:08:24,319 --> 00:08:26,519
Here's a pill.

172
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:27,439
You...

173
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,000
Give it to Miss Qiuying.

174
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,839
Then tell her,

175
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,399
she must remember this.

176
00:08:32,399 --> 00:08:33,480
Listen carefully inside the coffin.

177
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,399
The moment they close the lid,

178
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,200
put this in her mouth.

179
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:38,559
Got it?

180
00:08:40,639 --> 00:08:41,799
Don't ask why.

181
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,159
Just do as I say.

182
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:51,240
Here are two Eternal Lamps.

183
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:52,799
Find a way

184
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:54,960
to swap the Sorceress's Eternal Lamp

185
00:08:55,279 --> 00:08:56,200
with these two.

186
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:57,519
Got it?

187
00:08:57,639 --> 00:08:58,159
Got it.

188
00:08:59,080 --> 00:08:59,360
Good

189
00:08:59,679 --> 00:09:00,879
Now go do it.

190
00:09:01,639 --> 00:09:01,919
Okay.

191
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:02,840
Master

192
00:09:03,279 --> 00:09:03,759
Auntie Xiaoling

193
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:04,639
We're heading off then.

194
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,399
I'll see you out.

195
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:08,399
Auntie Xiaoling

196
00:09:08,919 --> 00:09:09,559
What's wrong?

197
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,399
You didn't fight with Master again, right?

198
00:09:14,639 --> 00:09:15,600
What nonsense.

199
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,600
I'm not taking the blame for that.

200
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:18,840
Where's Xiaolian?

201
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:20,240
Don't ask.

202
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,440
You two have big things to handle.

203
00:09:22,639 --> 00:09:23,120
Get going.

204
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:23,679
Let's go.

205
00:09:23,679 --> 00:09:24,039
Alright.

206
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:41,480
Mother...

207
00:09:42,559 --> 00:09:43,679
I don't want to marry him.

208
00:09:44,799 --> 00:09:45,879
I don't want to marry him!

209
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:48,240
My child...

210
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:51,399
Do something, will you!

211
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,399
Our daughter

212
00:09:53,759 --> 00:09:56,200
is going to be buried alive tonight.

213
00:09:57,399 --> 00:09:59,159
What can I possibly do?

214
00:09:59,519 --> 00:10:01,039
Aren't you the Mayor?

215
00:10:02,399 --> 00:10:03,960
Mayor my ass!

216
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:05,039
He's a Brigade Commander.

217
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:06,559
He's got these.

218
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:07,919
So what if he has guns?

219
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,159
I've got guns too!

220
00:10:09,919 --> 00:10:11,399
I'm usually the one pushing people around.

221
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:12,480
Who'd have thought,

222
00:10:12,759 --> 00:10:14,799
today we'd get pushed around ourselves.

223
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:16,519
I'm going to take them on right now!

224
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:18,559
Go!

225
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:19,799
Go on!

226
00:10:24,679 --> 00:10:25,720
Go!

227
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:26,879
Where's all that bravado now?

228
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:28,759
Brother-in-law.

229
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,519
I think about this whole thing...

230
00:10:30,519 --> 00:10:31,519
Who exactly are you fighting?

231
00:10:33,559 --> 00:10:34,440
Company Commander Shui.

232
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,240
I was just telling my brother-in-law,

233
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,639
I've got my eye on a nice house.

234
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,600
Don't have enough money.

235
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,960
So I told my brother-in-law,

236
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,799
let's pool our money and buy that house.

237
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:44,480
Right.

238
00:10:44,799 --> 00:10:45,960
Pool it, pool it.

239
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:47,559
Young Mistress, please

240
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,120
come with us.

241
00:10:51,679 --> 00:10:52,519
Qiuying!

242
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:56,639
Sis!

243
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:57,559
This...

244
00:11:00,639 --> 00:11:02,639
My daughter!

245
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,720
Let go of me!

246
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:09,759
I won't go!

247
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:12,639
What are you doing? Let go of me!

248
00:11:17,759 --> 00:11:18,120
What on earth...

249
00:11:20,399 --> 00:11:21,000
Qiuying

250
00:11:21,919 --> 00:11:22,759
Do you trust me?

251
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:40,919
Move out!

252
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:27,840
Stop.

253
00:12:42,039 --> 00:12:42,600
Dig.

254
00:12:43,399 --> 00:12:44,000
Dig!

255
00:12:46,399 --> 00:12:48,039
Oh, my daughter!

256
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:51,120
You wanted Dad to be County Magistrate.

257
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,919
But I haven't become County Magistrate yet,

258
00:12:53,919 --> 00:12:57,799
and now I'm a parent burying their child.

259
00:12:59,399 --> 00:13:00,440
My daughter...

260
00:13:01,399 --> 00:13:02,000
In-law.

261
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,080
You're crying too early.

262
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,240
She's not buried yet.

263
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:06,960
Alright.

264
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:07,960
The hour has come.

265
00:13:08,279 --> 00:13:09,559
Lift the coffin!

266
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,120
Why is it so heavy?
